      "id": 41094,
      "postNumber": 5,
      "createdAt": "2021-02-17T15:02:04.612Z",
      "author": "Helen (Helen)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/igor_tretiakov\">@Igor_Tretiakov</a>!</p>\n<p>Currently, our monday apps framework doesn’t yet support Subitems in the recipe builders for your integration recipe.</p>\n<p>However, I can absolutely see how useful and helpful this would be, so I would be more than happy to forward your feedback to our dev team for consideration.</p>\n<p>Custom automations are an internal feature and function pretty separately from the apps framework, which is why you’re seeing the ability there.</p>\n<p>Hope this helps!<br />\n-Helen</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 41155,
      "postNumber": 6,
      "createdAt": "2021-02-18T00:32:08.885Z",
      "author": "Igor_Tretiakov (Igor Tretiakov)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Thank you, Helen.</p>\n<p>I have the another question about building the integration recipe for Mirror column.</p>\n<p>The board with several mirror columns:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/2/29013fe4bba43bdf72c429449cbd44cb1fb2eabd.png\" title=\"Снимок экрана 2021-02-18 в 04.21.03\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/2/29013fe4bba43bdf72c429449cbd44cb1fb2eabd_2_690x121.png\" alt=\"Снимок экрана 2021-02-18 в 04.21.03\" width=\"690\" height=\"121\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Снимок экрана 2021-02-18 в 04.21.03</span><span class=\"informations\">2808×494 36 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Custom action:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/1/11f53833272de7aaecc3475b4acd261cb40d8ef7.png\" title=\"Снимок экрана 2021-02-18 в 04.23.37\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/1/11f53833272de7aaecc3475b4acd261cb40d8ef7_2_474x375.png\" alt=\"Снимок экрана 2021-02-18 в 04.23.37\" width=\"474\" height=\"375\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Снимок экрана 2021-02-18 в 04.23.37</span><span class=\"informations\">1708×1348 170 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/e/ef8f42282f7360a563bd95e36c3f5adbc3cb7bf0.png\" title=\"Снимок экрана 2021-02-18 в 04.24.50\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/e/ef8f42282f7360a563bd95e36c3f5adbc3cb7bf0_2_218x250.png\" alt=\"Снимок экрана 2021-02-18 в 04.24.50\" width=\"218\" height=\"250\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Снимок экрана 2021-02-18 в 04.24.50</span><span class=\"informations\">1092×1252 70.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Then I’m adding this custom integration to my board. There are zero mirror columns.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/8/842262672dae9d703c581e28b2b52803c048a5c8.png\" title=\"Снимок экрана 2021-02-18 в 04.21.47\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/8/842262672dae9d703c581e28b2b52803c048a5c8_2_345x70.png\" alt=\"Снимок экрана 2021-02-18 в 04.21.47\" width=\"345\" height=\"70\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Снимок экрана 2021-02-18 в 04.21.47</span><span class=\"informations\">2518×514 37.6 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>So what am I doing wrong?</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 41203,
      "postNumber": 7,
      "createdAt": "2021-02-18T13:00:09.442Z",
      "author": "Helen (Helen)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi Igor,</p>\n<p>Great question! The ability to choose columns that are unsupported in your action block (see below)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/e/e49ff934945f31147c60c44d3c9c46192134334f.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"293\" height=\"223\" /></p>\n<p>is actually a “bug” that our developers are working on within our current iteration. You are correct in that at this time, mirror columns are yet unsupported by our apps framework as well.</p>\n<p>This option to choose “Mirror” columns should be removed by the end of next week for selection.</p>\n<p>Sorry for the confusion!<br />\n-Helen</p>"
    }
